{"tid":2363354,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【美國大選】蓬佩奧與拜登國務卿人選布林肯討論交接 發文指會面「很有成果」","createTime":"2021-01-12T06:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T07:25:38.000Z","uid":377064,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"65146a0cf036dafdb1863956e49220dc49b409c4","tid":2363354,"uid":377064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:51:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210109/TPSUAATC3JFHTGWKDB3OZHVULA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210109%2FTPSUAATC3JFHTGWKDB3OZHVULA%2F&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJud6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=b1e4443e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210109%2FTPSUAATC3JFHTGWKDB3OZHVULA%2F&h=3cb6fd57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210109/TPSUAATC3JFHTGWKDB3OZHVULA/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國政權交接倒數，國務卿蓬佩奧周五與總統當選人拜登的國務卿提名人選布林肯（Antony Blinken）會晤，並承諾會平穩過渡權力。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧在Twitter發文指，為確保有序過渡及維護海外美國人的利益，兩人決定見面討論交接，「我們的會談很有成果，雙方將為了國家繼續在交接上好好合作」。<br />\n<br />\n原定上月中會面 因蓬佩奧自我隔離而取消<br />\n美媒早前報道蓬佩奧與布林肯原先計劃在上月17日見面，但前一天傳出蓬佩奧曾與武漢肺炎確診者接觸，決定自我隔離的消息。而在蓬佩奧隔離期間，布林肯仍於原定會面日期前往國務院聽取簡報並參與多項會議。<br />\n<br />\n58歲的布林肯外交資歷豐富，熟悉歐洲事務，他曾在前總統奧巴馬（Barack Obama）任內擔任副國務卿。在民主黨重獲參議院多數優勢下，布林肯的提名預料很快獲通過。<br />\n<br />\n布林肯日前也有回應本港50多名民主派人士遭警方以違反國安法拘捕一事，他指港府做法是侵犯勇敢提倡普世價值的人士，強調拜登和副總統當選人賀錦麗會站在港人一方，並反對北京打壓民主。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HeUHFx8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHeUHFx8.png&h=0fbbb718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法新社/中央社/《蘋果》資料室"},{"pid":"3bdea39cf19430215215559a39408b85b942389c","tid":2363354,"uid":377064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:51:47.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔好當pompeo係deep state<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2d50762abf9edb967dbccc46e0ddb4bd79481a","tid":2363354,"uid":377064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:57:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"17baa29ada10fb17f6bb010aaa59cdf4205af565","tid":2363354,"uid":377064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:58:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8aef9545dc0548a983420fc9ae52a2b3344eaa8e","tid":2363354,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T07:10:03.000Z","msg":"啲用字好有支那 feel<br />\n<br />\n親切友好的交談。（字面意思）<br />\n坦率交談。（分歧很大，無法溝通）<br />\n很有成果。（有爭論但未反面）<br />\n我們持保留態度。（我們拒絕同意）<br />\n我們尊重。（不完全同意）<br />\n嚴重關切。（可能要干預）<br />\n不要惹是生非。（別挑釁）"},{"pid":"b79d8808606f9b471e5c10fd211ad14ef857ba31","tid":2363354,"uid":348370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T07:10:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"66015aaba0af5d4a1d6152fd34b464780803b5b4","tid":2363354,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T07:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k9Kc2Tk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk9Kc2Tk.png&h=2dd4f290&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81f55d57d1b4972f56b390538c02195b85c25403","tid":2363354,"uid":384590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T07:12:44.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">一中</span></span>"},{"pid":"e4bf70bd266a1fc9075a3fff1d2b680f93b0e487","tid":2363354,"uid":377064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T07:25:03.000Z","msg":"反而pompeo個twitter比較和平，唔似得pence<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3fc2f5f993aa85f03b8b9a5dceddc2f9ef72b5","tid":2363354,"uid":377064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aef9545dc0548a983420fc9ae52a2b3344eaa8e","tid":2363354,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T07:10:03.000Z","msg":"啲用字好有支那 feel<br />\n<br />\n親切友好的交談。（字面意思）<br />\n坦率交談。（分歧很大，無法溝通）<br />\n很有成果。（有爭論但未反面）<br />\n我們持保留態度。（我們拒絕同意）<br />\n我們尊重。（不完全同意）<br />\n嚴重關切。（可能要干預）<br />\n不要惹是生非。（別挑釁）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T07:25:38.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}